      "author": "nothingislost",
      "description": "## 0.3.0\r\n  - Add hotkey support for loading specific workspaces\r\n    - This feature will create a command for every workspace in your vault, which can then be bound to hotkeys\r\n    - This feature supports renaming workspaces while maintaining the associated hotkey\r\n    - You can add these workspace load commands to cMenu and workspace renames will automatically update the cMenu button as well\r\n  - Add a data attribute to the body of the HTML document which indicates the currently active workspace name\r\n    - The selector looks like this: body[data-workspace-name=\"My Workspace\"]",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "0.3.0",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2021-09-24T17:49:50Z",
      "tag": "0.3.0"
